emerges from a\nconsideration of the causality constraint that is naturally imposed on both the\nreflected and transmitted wavepackets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Aug 2021 19:33:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
