ffic\nflow-density, the maximum traffic flow has been shown to be increased, and the\npoints in the congestion area have also been greatly reduced. Overall, the time\nrequired for individual vehicles was reduced.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Aug 2021 05:35:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Aug 2021 22:01:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-31"}
