10^{-10}M_\\odot$. We discuss the\nlimiting factors to perform these searches for each telescope type. We\ncalculate the rate of expected detectable microlensing events in the relevant\nmass range for the current and next-generation IACTs considering realistic\nsource parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Aug 2021 10:05:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
