elberg\nmechanism arises naturally in strings and the existence of a millicharge would\npoint to its string origin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Aug 2021 15:58:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 20:38:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
