he light quarks. The flavor dependence of the\nmass and wave-renormalization functions as well as their analytic behavior on\nthe complex momentum plane is studied and as an application we calculate the\nquark condensate and the pion's weak decay constant in the chiral limit. Both\nare in very good agreement with their reference values.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Aug 2021 05:55:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Nov 2021 19:05:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-02"}
